FA Street Rush Ultimate

Files
- index.html
- firebase-config.js

GitHub Pages upload
1. Upload both files into one folder/repo.
2. Open GitHub Pages on that folder/repo.
3. The game works immediately with local save, daily reward, missions, shop, and local ranking.

Online ranking
- This build is Firebase-ready, but live online ranking needs a real Firebase project.
- Put your Firebase values into firebase-config.js
- Then connect your ranking save/load logic where you want to extend it.

What is included now
- Improved collision logic
- Jump and slide gameplay
- Lobby
- Missions
- Daily reward
- Shop and skins
- Local ranking
- Firebase-ready config file
